否会成为现实，那么这次交易是购买你的第一双鞋的好时机。或者更换您留在火车上的那双。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> AirPods Pro刚推出时我们给了<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218-130048292.html">88分</a>。 Engadget 的 Billy Steele 赞扬了有效的主动降噪 (ANC) 功能，并将环境声音模式称为市场上最好的模式之一。此外，它们可与您的所有 Apple 设备无缝配合，提供快速配对、快速设备切换和免提 Siri 支持。与前几代 Pro 相比，音频本身更丰富、更有深度、更清晰。</p><p>所有这些都使我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">购买指南</a>中为iPhone命名了最好的无线耳塞。当然，它们不适用于非 Apple 设备。我们目前从Android手机指南的首选是<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL0dvb2dsZS1QaXhlbC1CdWRzLVByby1IZWFkcGhvbmVzL2RwL0IwQjFON1NHTVo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tNWZjLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIzNGE1NmEyNi0wYzAwLTQyOWQtODMxZC1kNzUzNzRmYzE1ZmQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAWmCy59NYaWVKNLFhs_57FwrJztfXMNqj2uQDLmMGvYJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoogle-Pixel-Buds-Pro-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB0B1N7SGMZ" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Google-Pixel-Buds-Pro-Headphones/dp/B0B1N7SGMZ?th=1">Google Pixel Buds Pro</a> ，目前在亚马逊折扣30％后，目前在亚马逊上降至140美元。</p><p>在 Twitter 上<em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a><em>并</em><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的科技交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初出现在https://www.engadget.com/apples-second-generation-airpods-pro-are-are-are-back-down-to-their-their-lowest-price-price-ever-1655823.html？ ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apples-second-generation-airpods-pro-are-back-down-to-th